data.description: Tucked away with a country feel, on a dead end road, you will find the perfect setting to sit on the back deck or the front patio and drink your morning coffee. This home sits on 2.5 acres that is perfect to watch your childen or grandchildren run and play. Theres plenty of open space for activites, yet still surrounded on both sides with a wooded area that is great for privacy. With the open floor concept, this 3 bedroom 2 bath home is perfect for family interaction or privacy if wanted as the master bedroom is split from the two additional bedrooms. The master bath offers a whirlpool bath tub, perfect for soaking and a walk in closet. There is a separate shower as well. The dining / living area have vaulted ceiling  It has a spacious laundry room that you can hang jackets or backpacks. It also offers the convenience of entering into a tile area before walking into the home, which is perfect for those days you come in with a little dirt on your shoes. Lots of counter space in the kitchen and new appliances make entertaining easy and fun! So bring your things and come make memories in this beautiful atmosphere! Since you might a little extra space for the mower and such, there is a 24x24 shop here too! It's conventiently insulated and wired with a large garage door.  Seller will be taking the storage building behind the shop.
